Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This peculiar story\Nbegan on a blazing hot day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Out of the blue, I got an e-mail\Nfrom an old acquaintance of mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was no explanation,\Nand the message was very terse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All it said was,\N"Seek the holy beast of Anzan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I am where the four gods meet."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The message came from a guy named Pao,\Nwho I had lost touch with long ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was leery, to say the least.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I decided to look into\Nhis current whereabouts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pao's background was unknown,\Nbut he had a reputation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as one of the three greatest\Nfeng shui masters on Mars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when I finally managed to\Nlocate him, it was not in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you couldn't have sent me\Nthat message from here, could you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who visits from\Nthe inauspicious door...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,receives word from the heavens\Nand will lead me to the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the pakua said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you aiming at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck of a place for target practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Idiot.\N- Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a\Npretty close one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad just you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look over there.\NJet's got a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fine romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too young for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot dog bun, not too young!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's got a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, afraid she's too old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oldy and moldy, history, mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao's little girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't expect you\Nto be this old already, Meifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you don't remember this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were this little, I met you\Nwhen I was visiting your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you friends with my father?\NHow did you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an acquaintance.\NIt's been ten years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I sure am sorry he got killed\Nin that transport accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He was on his way to Jupiter.\NThey told me it was very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a hyperspace fluctuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You Jet's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have a thing for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All is fair in love and war!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet, why were you\Nat my father's grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No one outside the family\Nknows about his accident yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Message: "Seek the holy beast of Anzan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am where the four gods meet."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a message that was\Nsent here by your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- When?\N- Three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It means he knew!\NCan you help me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}has{\i0} to be!\NIt's about the sun stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun stone? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The direction, the day,\N{\i1}and{\i0} the time you arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,were all the best\Ncombination for feng shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you're on a quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What... kind of quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sun stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Jet, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yeah, we'll have it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- So how's the boss taking it?\N- Uh... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- That can't be real good.\N- Not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't owe any favors\Nto Pao or the girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could've just blown the whole thing off,\Nbut something made me hang on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was all the\Ndangling questions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why'd Pao send a message\Nto me before he died?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four gods and the\Nholy beast of Anzan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did all that mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And who were the guys who tried\Nto shoot us at the gravesite?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then there was Meifa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that gypsy scarf\Nand all that spirit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This universe is composed\Nof the three chis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the chi of heaven,\Nthe energy that comes from the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And one is the chi of earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the power that comes from\Nthe planet we all live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the last one\Nis the magnetic chi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes from\Nliving organisms like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean human chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, from the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Each body produces\Na magnetic field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which interacts with the\Nmagnetic field of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what creates\Nthe energy we all use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal feng shui is the science\Nthat reads these natural energies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and applies them to everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ice cream.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal feng shui...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that any different than\Nplain old fortunetelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fortunetelling," indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunetellers only predict and foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But feng shui is active.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the power to turn\Nbad luck into good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if you were a powerful\Nfeng shui master like my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realized that I never spent any\Ntime like this talking with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not old enough to\Nbe your father, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, if anything,\NI could be your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, that would\Nbe bad, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Open foot, insert mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'd be more like\Nyour older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ice cream.\N- Ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream cone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe "Anzan"\Nrefers to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mountain Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,White tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake and tortoise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Red phoenix!\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The zenith cross.\NIt's the four gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here. It's the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.\NThey're right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, Jet. The sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A black rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get outta here.\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Skeezers!\N- Stupid suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A bottle of lao chu.\NI don't need a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm gonna tell you that?\NNot a chance, baldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from the Blue Snake!\NWe're on assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're syndicate scumbags.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you following us around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even if you kill me,\NI can't tell you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Pao! We were after him,\Nbut he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We tracked the message he sent.\NThat's what led us to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the low end, so that's\Nall the information they gave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these cheesy glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My father... He's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The words in Pao's message\Nhad led us to the stone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But did that mean\NPao was still alive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seemed he wanted us\Nto have this stone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why? What were we\Nsupposed to do with it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every time we solved a mystery,\Nit just led to new ones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darker and more unsettling\Nthan the ones before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And our only clue\Nwas the stone itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I decided to run some tests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a piece of the moon from\Nthat gate accident fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Feng shui masters\Ncall it the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, all the time-space\Nfluctuations were absorbed by the stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,condensing a tremendous amount of energy\Nwhich has been amplified by the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a plain old\Nmoon rock to me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how much is it worth\Nif we try to sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You two smoke outside\Nif you need to smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Excuse me, but you\Nalways smoke in here, Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is now a non-smoking area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're joking around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like I'm joking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you gonna\Ndo with this sun stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My father had something\Nin mind, but what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ein! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The luopan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't spin like that,\NI took the magnet off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, my father has\Na sun stone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The two stones resonate\Nto one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we follow the energy,\Nit'll lead us to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} why Pao wanted\Nyou to find this stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but... I don't know why\Nhe sent that message to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a dangerous combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The more righteous a guy\Nwas back in his youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the more likely he is to fall for some\Nyoung thing when he gets older.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely. Men are\Nextremely predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My father believed in universal\Nfeng shui, and in nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't believe in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So my mother left him,\Nand she took me with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I'm sure that\Nhe could have found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't have been\Nall that hard, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But he never tried once\Nin all those years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a good reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the reason why\Nthose men were after my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're bad men!\NHow did they know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me the truth, Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna know who\Nmy father really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao... was a consultant\Nfor a major syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the real story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He leaked some inside information to me\Nback when I was a detective with ISSP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he was looking for a way out,\Nand he thought I could help him find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried, but... it's impossible for someone\Nto leave when they know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you join a syndicate,\Nthey own you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cross them, they take\Nrevenge on you and your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's what\Nhe was trying to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can ask him yourself\Nif the sun stone leads us to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... yeah... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- And the radar?\N- Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be.\NI'm sure this is the right spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got company!\N- These guys never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, Faye, deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}your{\i0} little party, Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle stations, or die with the ship.\NThose are your options.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's called "giving," Faye.\NThink of us as fairy godparents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to grant the\Nprincess a very special wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So these must be\Nthe evil stepsisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! They're trying to scare us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Spike, come back in!{\i0}\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}New plan. Looks like if we apply\Nenough energy to the sun stone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we can draw out the\Nforces trapped inside it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Great, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we take our shot.\NAll or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're gonna do,\Ndo it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike, hit it with\Nyour plasma cannon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm shooting a rock now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like you made it in time, Jet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa... It's been a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao, you're in an\Nunstable force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no oxygen left here, anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sent you that message\Nbecause I hoped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'd manage to bring\Nmy daughter out here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're saying\Nyou used feng shui
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach us and bring us out here\Naccording to {\i1}your{\i0} will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}not{\i0} right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't in control\Nof this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Meifa is here now because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because she wanted to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You might be right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I gave myself\Ntoo much credit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa, it's so wonderful\Nto see you one last time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for all those years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. It hurt so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I don't know\Nif it was a good thing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or a bad thing that we\Nbrought her out there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that is how this\Npeculiar case ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa went back home to Mars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our no smoking area became\Na smoking zone again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And life returned to the same\Ndaily routine just like before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One thing has changed, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I read the news,\NI never check the horoscopes anymore.{\i0}
